They specify on their website and on the front door of the store itself that the place closes at 2am. But when me and a bunch of friends wanted to order and eat in at 11pm, they said "sorry we're closed, come back tomorrow". My friends and I we're super confused and tried asking if we could order take out. They refused, Because they had claimed that they already cleaned the grill and put everything away and that there not interested in cleaning it again. So instead they decided to kick us out and close 3 hours early. Absolutely ridiculous place. Complete disregard for customer service. Don't recommend it to anyone looking for a late night snack or pretty much anything for that matter.
